item.title: Go Mod Init
item.author: strawbreey@qq.com (strawbreey)
item.description: go Mod Help $ go help mod Go mod provides access to operations on modules. Note that support for modules is built into all the go commands, not just 'go mod'. For example, day-to-day adding, removing, upgrading, and downgrading of dependencies should be done using 'go get'. See 'go help modules' for an overview of module functionality. Usage: go mod <command> [arguments] The commands are: download download modules to local
